个人简介
			
			





&nbsp;任浩然HaoranRen
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

浙江大学地球科学学院地质与地球物理研究所，讲师，硕士研究生导师，求是青年学者。


Lecturer,MasterStudentSupervisorandDistiguishedYoungScholar,InZhejiangUniversity.
InstituteofGeologyandGeophysics,&nbsp;SchoolofEarthSciences,ZhejiangUniversity
